id: pm-114v
title: "pm claim --next: atomically claim the next actionable item so parallel agents each get distinct work"
description: "Companion to pm-8t5x. pm next + pm claim as separate steps race under parallel agents: all N agents get the same recommendation and N-1 fail their claim. Add an atomic recommend+claim with bounded retry over next-ranked candidates so each parallel agent receives a distinct item. Idea originated in the 2026-07-03 concurrency review (recorded inside pm-8t5x's fix sketch); promoted to its own tracked Feature by the 2026-07-04 metadata review."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 2
