acceptance_criteria: "pm claim --next claims a distinct item per parallel agent (stress-verified, zero double-grants); bounded candidate retry on already_claimed_by; output includes pm next rationale; wired across MCP/contracts/completion/docs per new-command checklist"
parent: pm-dj98
risk: medium
confidence: medium
resolution: Added atomic ranked claim-next selection with bounded conflict retries and if-available behavior.
expected_result: Parallel agents can claim distinct recommended work through the SDK-backed CLI without a list-then-claim race.
actual_result: "claim --next ranks actionable candidates, retries ownership conflicts, returns recommendation evidence, and passed concurrency and packed-install acceptance tests."
